name: koding-dnode-protocol

scripts.prepublish: rm -fr build && mkdir -p build && coffee -p -b index.coffee > build/index.js

readme:
# dnode-protocol

[dnode](https://github.com/substack/dnode) implementation.

This package exports `build/index.js`; to transpile coffeescript sources into js, type in:

```
npm run prepublish
```
